7.000Z","msg":"但我真係做唔到 我唔係冇試過同佢示好<br />\n但永遠我做乜佢都潑我冷水<br />\n好冇癮姐"},{"pid":"f463c743e3d546e41853a37a2606c00609902f62","tid":545481,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"我同你都幾似 一開頭會駁下佢嘴 <br />\n後尾唔想再嗌交就索性唔講野 成日一個人喺間房到 <br />\n跟住佢就話我自閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗可能伯母都係想撩下你傾計 但講野唔係好叻 用錯方法姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又可能覺得直接咁講你畫得靚會肉麻？(我對住親嘅人有時會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"070ad1cc2c644a75536428b7f23bb41e9fe17d59","tid":545481,"uid":135016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7683c5a826e09d7781f7f394794ffc08dfb4da3","tid":545481,"uid":38744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過你老母<br />\n<br />\n未必係想姪你 想同你互動下姐<br />\n<br />\n既然你知佢係錫你 咁佢姪你做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n放開一點，就用你啲例子<br />\n<br />\n佢話你減黎晒氣 你啲朋友呃你<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">你咪話佢地呃得黎開心啊 我鍾意聽喎<br />\n咁減左少少就要獎下自己架啦 冇話晒唔晒氣</span><br />\n<br />\n其實做到家人 你地係有一定嘅緣份 唔好輕易就搬走 更何況呢啲好雞毛蒜皮咋喎</blockquote><br />\n傻啦<br />\n你以為咁講完就冇事咩<br />\n咪又係會繼續窒你<br />\n你咁諗好似好正面<br />\n但有啲人真係乜都窒住晒<br />\n你用咩方法應對佢佢都係會窒你<br />\n把口係唔會收<br />\n長年累月點頂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"我試過示好 因為唔想爆佢<br />\n好驚自己會講啲好難聽嘅說話<br />\n但一直忍自己又好難受"},{"pid":"87f3c251522936becf79ba8daf6e39e773a8d1ac","tid":545481,"uid":135016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d937a53f6e5a8dcf5af002d11c5c9d37eacb439d","tid":545481,"uid":164863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好想的起心肝唔理老豆老母<br />\n但係問心又做唔出<br />\n但深一層又對自己好委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"就係咁啦！！<br />\n所以好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562ead0f0b7d6e1fdd2c6967a54accc2d587ff67","tid":545481,"uid":124058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"我都好辛苦<br />\n我同公公婆婆住 佢地好錫我<br />\n但成日都發我脾氣 又無乜溝通<br />\n我個心都好錫佢地<br />\n但行為上真係無能為力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得一齊住好大壓力<br />\n少少野都問<br />\n開一開房門就問我想做咩去邊<br />\n我知係關心<br />\n但真係好大壓力"},{"pid":"2ddaad51cfbec24b2f1c0894bd6d5b8e1d6a1594","tid":545481,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"當你有一日做人老豆老母<br />\n<br />\n你D仔女咪又係咁樣對你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇開D,唔好咁介意,見一日少一日,到你嫁左出去,或者同老婆搬左出去住,你就會明點解老豆老母咁煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de48591d582c18499a601fc53e8af22746b51ba","tid":545481,"uid":138981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57341c179e0a2ca9b69ff3426c1b4661f96c622f","tid":545481,"uid":135016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b752145790acfd69b55d86081ab20da678de810","tid":545481,"uid":138981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c15eff8cb8b062a6629c96d5b9bf32efbda4cbb5","tid":545481,"uid":135016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"仲當我細路咁管住晒真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一返嚟住關係就差"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"之前決定出去讀書係因為當時佢管住晒<br />\n好想脫離吓<br />\n點知而家返到黎又係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"宜家完全係相見難同住又難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之我就一定搬架喇 再住喺度只會關係更差"},{"pid":"bfdc1005c46a04ffb1064841abfa2b607da6a5fd","tid":545481,"uid":105500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"我就快三十<br />\n一直都想搬出去自己住<br />\n但屋企得老母一個<br />\n如果我搬埋就得返佢自己<br />\n佢仲要係冇返工果d<br />\n成個生活得返我一個<br />\n我唔忍心所以一路同住<br />\n雖然同住冇咩問題<br />\n不過年紀越大就會想搬出去"},{"pid":"9163d4a9b24e910c7c0a43b36eea91a60d0aadea","tid":545481,"uid":135016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f463c743e3d546e41853a37a2606c00609902f62","tid":545481,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"我同你都幾似 一開頭會駁下佢嘴 <br />\n後尾唔想再嗌交就索性唔講野 成日一個人喺間房到 <br />\n跟住佢就話我自閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗可能伯母都係想撩下你傾計 但講野唔係好叻 用錯方法姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又可能覺得直接咁講你畫得靚會肉麻？(我對住親嘅人有時會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"我唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之而家自閉對我黎講係屋企係最舒服<br />\n唔係唔想同佢地傾吓閒計<br />\n但唔想再比佢姪住晒"},{"pid":"0228564c25da56ca2294f0e5e4a489b7a4221e61","tid":545481,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"孝順下啦不肖子<br />\n<br />\n自己諗下有幾耐無打過俾老母單純係為咗關心佢做緊咩"},{"pid":"ac6d48a44f9fc4b954b6609cf97451d907151c14","tid":545481,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f78af277efd684d5263d8c3cbbf26e8571fa9a7d","tid":545481,"uid":135016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92d99c9547beaed2c6d0